Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.75,Default-3,,0,0,0,,过去与现在都已凋零\N{\rEng}"The past and present wilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.66,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我充盈它们 又将它们掏空\N{\rEng}"I have filled them, emptied them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.53,Default-3,,0,0,0,,然后继续去充盈未来的下一折页\N{\rEng}"and proceed to fill my next fold of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.75,Default-3,,0,0,0,,云端的倾听者啊！有何秘密要向我倾诉？\N{\rEng}"Listener up there! What have you to confide to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.67,Default-3,,0,0,0,,当我细嗅暮色时 直视我的面庞\N{\rEng}"Look in my face while I snuff the sidle of evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:33.76,Default-3,,0,0,0,,放心说吧 无人能闻得见 我只多留片刻\N{\rEng}"Talk honestly, no one else hears you, and I stay only a minute longer."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:36.24,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我是否自相矛盾？\N{\rEng}"Do I contradict myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.77,Default-3,,0,0,0,,好吧 那我就自相矛盾\N{\rEng}"Very well then, I contradict myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.60,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我心疆无限 我包罗万象\N{\rEng}I am large, I contain multitudes."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.77,Default-3,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.25,Default-3,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.89,Default-3,,0,0,0,,什么事让你打断惠特曼的诗？\N{\rEng}Clearly something more interesting than Whitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.59,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是加州 那又地震了\N{\rEng}California. There was another earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:54.98,Default-3,,0,0,0,,从圣巴巴拉到弗雷斯诺一大片地都没了...\N{\rEng}A huge chunk's gone from Santa Barbara to Fresno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.55,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-太可怕了 -...沉入大海了 \N{\rEng}-It's fucking crazy. -Into the ocean.
