Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.44,Default-3,,0,0,0,,格斯\N{\rEng}Gus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.66,Default-3,,0,0,0,,哦 嘿 马蒂\N{\rEng}Oh. Hey, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.97,Default-3,,0,0,0,,怎么不开车了？\N{\rEng}Where's your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:22.30,Default-3,,0,0,0,,车 车停在半山腰了 好几百辆车都扔路上了\N{\rEng}It's... it's on, it's on the sidewalk halfway down Main Street Hill with a hundred others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.87,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我只好步行\N{\rEng}I finally just had to turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.69,Default-3,,0,0,0,,该死 我走了\N{\rEng}Fuck it, I walked...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.22,Default-3,,0,0,0,,猜我走了多远？ 这有五公里了吧？\N{\rEng}What do you think it is, like, three miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:29.18,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我走了将近五公里\N{\rEng}I just walked three miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.39,Default-3,,0,0,0,,哦 你是这要去学校吧 等下\N{\rEng}Oh, you're going to school. Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:35.22,Default-3,,0,0,0,,呃 我想下 你得绕 你得绕\N{\rEng}Uh, real quick, you gotta, you gotta go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.23,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你得绕道走11号公路\N{\rEng}listen to me, you gotta go out Route 11
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.58,Default-3,,0,0,0,,然后在转到19号公路\N{\rEng}and then hook back on, on, on 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.84,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是呀 路上会很堵\N{\rEng}Yeah. There's gonna be plenty of traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.32,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你大概得绕至少30公里\N{\rEng}You gotta go out at least 20 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.80,Default-3,,0,0,0,,运气好中午能到\N{\rEng}You might make it before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.24,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-别指望早到 -发生了什么事？ \N{\rEng}-I wouldn't count on it. -What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.46,Default-3,,0,0,0,,市场街和主街交叉那有大地坑\N{\rEng}Giant sinkhole opened up on Market and Main.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.55,Default-3,,0,0,0,,老兄 陷得太大了\N{\rEng}Man, the-the thing, it, uh, it's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.81,Default-3,,0,0,0,,要么是降雨导致的\N{\rEng}All the rain probably had something to do with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.59,Default-3,,0,0,0,,要么是缺乏维护\N{\rEng}lack of maintenance maybe more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.90,Default-3,,0,0,0,,至少轮不到我去修\N{\rEng}But it's not my department, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.95,Default-3,,0,0,0,,但是 坑下面得有二十多辆车吧\N{\rEng}But, yeah, there's, there's gotta be 20 cars at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:05.34,Default-3,,0,0,0,,那些车里的人 永远上不来了\N{\rEng}And some of the people in some of those cars, they ain't comin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.21,Default-3,,0,0,0,,老天 我昨天下班就堵在那里\N{\rEng}Jesus, I was, I was just there last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.74,Default-3,,0,0,0,,堵在那好久\N{\rEng}backed up in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.52,Default-3,,0,0,0,,幸好你今早不在那里\N{\rEng}Thank God you weren't there this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.13,Default-3,,0,0,0,,听说加州的事了吧\N{\rEng}I assume you know about California.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.83,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我今早没看电视\N{\rEng}I didn't turn on the TV this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.05,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-难怪 -有什么新闻吗？ \N{\rEng}-Oh! -Is there something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.01,Default-3,,0,0,0,,都沉下去了\N{\rEng}The, the rest of it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.53,Default-3,,0,0,0,,电视说北加州20%还尚存\N{\rEng}I-I mean, th-they're saying that 20% of Northern California is hanging in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.32,Default-3,,0,0,0,,实际也许还剩10%\N{\rEng}which probably means, what, 10%?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:30.24,Default-3,,0,0,0,,但是粮食产区都没了\N{\rEng}But the food-producing regions are... they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:32.19,Default-3,,0,0,0,,中西部被烧成个焦土\N{\rEng}And with the Midwest turning to charcoal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.89,Default-3,,0,0,0,,佛州又被水淹\N{\rEng}and Florida flooding, that's like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:38.37,Default-3,,0,0,0,,全国粮仓都没了\N{\rEng}all the food-producing regions in the country just gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.77,Default-3,,0,0,0,,欧洲的情况也差不多\N{\rEng}And the same thing with Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.33,Default-3,,0,0,0,,亚洲也在闹饥荒\N{\rEng}I mean, it's famine time in Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.77,Default-3,,0,0,0,,听说那死了一百万人\N{\rEng}There's a million people dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.37,Default-3,,0,0,0,,他们管它叫做 树...树疫\N{\rEng}They're saying it's the bub-bublonic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.60,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-树疫病 -鼠疫 \N{\rEng}-bubonic plague. -Bubonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.56,Default-3,,0,0,0,,对 鼠...鼠疫\N{\rEng}Bu-Bubonic plague. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.86,Default-3,,0,0,0,,还有蜜蜂 十多年前就不正常\N{\rEng}And the bees, I mean, they were in trouble a decade ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.34,Default-3,,0,0,0,,但现在所有蜜蜂都没了\N{\rEng}but they're completely gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:54.04,Default-3,,0,0,0,,也许南美洲还有几个蜂巢吧\N{\rEng}I mean, there's a couple of hives or whatever down in South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.96,Default-3,,0,0,0,,但不产蜂蜜\N{\rEng}but there ain't no honey, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:59.74,Default-3,,0,0,0,,没有这些小虫虫 怎么给剩下的庄稼授粉呢\N{\rEng}And without those little guys, like, what's gonna pollinate all the crops we have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.79,Default-3,,0,0,0,,要我说 我可...\N{\rEng}I mean, I can't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.14,Default-3,,0,0,0,,先打住 稍后聊\N{\rEng}Excuse me. One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.44,Default-3,,0,0,0,,哦 哦 好\N{\rEng}Yeah, yeah. That's-that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.31,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是 安 安德莉娅吗？\N{\rEng}A-Andrea? Are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:07.19,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你是中西部信托银行的安德莉娅吗？\N{\rEng}are you Andrea from Midwest Trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.23,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我是菲莉西娅·安德森的丈夫\N{\rEng}I'm Felicia Anderson's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.41,Default-3,,0,0,0,,实际上 是前夫\N{\rEng}Ex, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.93,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我觉得你和小菲互相认识\N{\rEng}I think you and Fel know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.72,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我们之前在大卫家聚会时见过\N{\rEng}We met at a, a, a game night at David's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.83,Default-3,,0,0,0,,几晚游戏聚会\N{\rEng}A few game nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.20,Default-3,,0,0,0,,对 记得\N{\rEng}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.81,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你想干什么？\N{\rEng}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.07,Default-3,,0,0,0,,车堵在路上 我刚走了半天\N{\rEng}I just had a long walk, and my car is stuck,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:25.42,Default-3,,0,0,0,,而银行 斜了\N{\rEng}and the bank is, it's leaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.83,Default-3,,0,0,0,,斜了？\N{\rEng}Leaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.24,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:31.24,Default-3,,0,0,0,,银行就在地坑旁边\N{\rEng}It's on the edge of the sinkhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.99,Default-3,,0,0,0,,估计我的职业生涯到此为止\N{\rEng}Guess that's the end of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:36.17,Default-3,,0,0,0,,嘿 你们银行上头那广告牌是啥意思\N{\rEng}Hey, I'm curious about the billboard on the bank building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.48,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-你看到了吗？ -怎么能躲得过？ \N{\rEng}-Have you seen it? -How could I miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.86,Default-3,,0,0,0,,那广告还出现在电视上\N{\rEng}And I saw the ads too, on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.21,Default-3,,0,0,0,,电视不再播卖车卖家具的广告了\N{\rEng}No more ads for cars or discount furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:47.61,Default-3,,0,0,0,,只播“感谢查尔斯·克兰兹39年来的非凡岁月 谢谢你 查克”\N{\rEng}Just, "Charles Krantz, 39 great years. Thanks, Chuck."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.53,Default-3,,0,0,0,,他不是你银行的人？\N{\rEng}So, he doesn't work at the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.40,Default-3,,0,0,0,,他不是从你银行退休？\N{\rEng}He's not retiring from the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.10,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我根本不认识这个人\N{\rEng}I don't know Charles Krantz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:59.93,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我觉得这就是个恶搞 玩行为艺术\N{\rEng}I think it's just a prank. Performance art.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.51,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你保重\N{\rEng}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.51,Default-3,,0,0,0,,他们看起来像是灾民\N{\rEng}They look like refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:11.71,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.39,Default-3,,0,0,0,,至少大家不再惊慌失措了\N{\rEng}No one looks that concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:18.17,Default-3,,0,0,0,,那又怎样？\N{\rEng}What good would that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.69,Default-3,,0,0,0,,刚开始大家都惊慌失措\N{\rEng}All was concerned at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.52,Default-3,,0,0,0,,还记得那些抗议吗？\N{\rEng}Remember the protests?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.39,Default-3,,0,0,0,,还记得他们推倒白宫的围栏吗？\N{\rEng}You remember they knocked over the fence at the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.31,Default-3,,0,0,0,,记得他们向那些学生开枪吗？\N{\rEng}and all those students got shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.05,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-是的 -还有俄罗斯政府被推翻 \N{\rEng}-Yeah. -And the overthrow of the Russian government.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.66,Default-3,,0,0,0,,巴基斯坦和印度间的四日战争\N{\rEng}You got the Four Day War between Pakistan and India
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:35.97,Default-3,,0,0,0,,还有他妈的德国火山喷发\N{\rEng}and the fucking... the volcano in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:39.44,Default-3,,0,0,0,,德国火山还能喷发 太扯了\N{\rEng}There was a volcano in Germany. That's, that's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.98,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我们自我安慰“一切都会过去的”\N{\rEng}And we just kept saying, "Oh, it's gonna blow over."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:45.69,Default-3,,0,0,0,,看来过不去的 对吧？\N{\rEng}That doesn't look to be happening, though, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.46,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:52.33,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我觉得自杀的人最终会减少\N{\rEng}I think that suicides will slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:57.95,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我觉得人们最终会等待\N{\rEng}I think people will just...wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:01.08,Default-3,,0,0,0,,等什么？\N{\rEng}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.15,Default-3,,0,0,0,,等结局\N{\rEng}The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:08.02,Default-3,,0,0,0,,万物的大结局\N{\rEng}This is the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:11.11,Default-3,,0,0,0,,{\rNote\fs10}库伯勒-罗丝悲伤模型五阶段：否认 愤怒 恳求 沮丧 接受{\r}\N我们正处在 {\u1}悲伤模型{\u0} 第五阶段\N{\rEng}I mean, we're, we're going through the five stages of grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:15.46,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？咱们到了最后阶段\N{\rEng}Don't you get it? I mean, we just, we just landed on the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.50,Default-3,,0,0,0,,接受\N{\rEng}Acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:25.38,Default-3,,0,0,0,,等待 才是最难熬的\N{\rEng}The waiting...I think that's the hardest part.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:28.63,Default-3,,0,0,0,,灾难不打声招呼就冒出来了\N{\rEng}And the whole thing, it just, it-it came out of nowhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:31.29,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我是说 大家早知道有自然环境问题\N{\rEng}I mean, everyone knew there was trouble with the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:34.81,Default-3,,0,0,0,,即便是右翼疯子也私下里心知肚明\N{\rEng}I mean, I think even the right-wing nutjobs were secretly, they got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.39,Default-3,,0,0,0,,但现在\N{\rEng}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:39.33,Default-3,,0,0,0,,现在这些\N{\rEng}this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:45.43,Default-3,,0,0,0,,现在这些不过是各种屁事的集合\N{\rEng}this is just 60 different varieties of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:48.91,Default-3,,0,0,0,,屁事来的太快了\N{\rEng}It's just so much shit that happened fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:53.18,Default-3,,0,0,0,,现在一年都十四个月了\N{\rEng}It's like a year, man. Fourteen months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:57.04,Default-3,,0,0,0,,倒霉啊\N{\rEng}Sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:03.52,Default-3,,0,0,0,,是啊 倒霉啊\N{\rEng}Yeah. Sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:09.63,Default-3,,0,0,0,,飞机写字\N{\rEng}Skywriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:15.19,Default-3,,0,0,0,,长大后就再也没见过这种事\N{\rEng}I haven't seen one of those since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:14.81,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,100)\frz-22\fs26\i1\fsp12\blur0.5\1c&HAFB992&}谢谢你 亠亠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:22.08,Default-3,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:27.57,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我也想问同样的问题\N{\rEng}My sentiments... exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.71,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,100)\frz-22\fs26\i1\fsp12\blur0.5\1c&HAFB992&}谢谢你 查克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:38.18,Note,,0,0,0,,{\move(20,100,300,100)\fsp2\1c&H22A2C2&\shad1\bord1}谢谢你 查克！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:40.83,Note,,0,0,0,,{\move(20,80,230,80)\fsp2\1c&H5CA179&\shad1\bord1}街头艺人万岁
