Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.69,Note,,0,0,0,,{\move(20,80,230,80)\fsp2\1c&H202F75&\2c00222222\3c00222222\shad1\bord1}查克我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:48.13,Note,,0,0,0,,{\move(20,80,230,80)\fsp2\1c&H1196C0&\2c00222222\3c00222222\shad1\bord1}查克yyds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:56.08,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(100, 100)\fsp2\1c&H0C91BA&\shad1\bord1}爱你 查克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:02.42,Default-3,,0,0,0,,喂 喂 喂  你上哪去了？\N{\rEng}Whoa, whoa, whoa, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:05.73,Default-3,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？我跑过来的\N{\rEng}Are you kidding? I had to run here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:08.78,Default-3,,0,0,0,,路全堵了 一半人把车都仍路上了\N{\rEng}The traffic's insane, and half the cars are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:09.91,Default-3,,0,0,0,,温斯顿医生跑了\N{\rEng}Dr. Winston's MIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:11.60,Default-3,,0,0,0,,-什么意思？ -你没听错 \N{\rEng}-What? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:13.95,Default-3,,0,0,0,,他今天早上过来看了一圈转头就走了\N{\rEng}He walked in this morning, and he looked around and he walked out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.48,Default-3,,0,0,0,,再也找不到他了\N{\rEng}And now I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.50,0:24:17.44,Default-3,,0,0,0,,他把对讲机都扔门口了\N{\rEng}He dropped his pager when he walked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:19.74,Default-3,,0,0,0,,好 那我来开刀\N{\rEng}Okay. I'll scrub in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:22.09,Default-3,,0,0,0,,床位都空了\N{\rEng}The beds are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:25.68,Default-3,,0,0,0,,病人基本都自己走出去了 我把最后一个扶出去的\N{\rEng}Most of them walked out. I-I-I transferred the last of the stable ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.70,0:24:30.09,Default-3,,0,0,0,,但是 菲莉西娅 有点怪事\N{\rEng}But, Felicia, there's something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:33.57,Default-3,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.27,0:24:47.46,Default-3,,0,0,0,,机子坏了吗？\N{\rEng}What's wrong with the monitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.49,0:24:51.41,Default-3,,0,0,0,,这就是怪事 不只这一台\N{\rEng}That's the thing, it-it's, it's not just that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.64,0:25:18.11,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我搞不懂 小菲 搞不懂\N{\rEng}I don't know, Fel. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.13,0:25:22.59,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我 我也不想待在这了\N{\rEng}I mean... I might want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.61,0:25:24.85,Default-3,,0,0,0,,我想回家\N{\rEng}I might wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.87,0:25:29.09,Default-3,,0,0,0,,没必要再待在这了\N{\rEng}I don't think I need to be here anymore.
